After publishing the release:

1. Open the release page you just created.
2. Rightclick on the `app-release.apk` link under **Assets**.
3. Copy the link address.

It will look like:

- `https://github.com/Swastigit2005/Naari-Suraksha/releases/download/v1.0.0/app-release.apk`

You can share **this URL** directly with users; when they open it, the APK downloads.

